title: Updated Two Bedroom Apartment in New Hope!
posting_body: ['Hidden Creek Apartments features everything you love about a brand new apartment with the quality construction and sizable floor plans typically found in older buildings.', 'Short distance to shops at west end, northeast Minneapolis and downtown.', 'All new upgrades including huge kitchens, featuring mocha cabinets, granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, gas cooking ranges (for all you gourmet chefs out there), new hardwood style flooring, paint, lighting, blinds and carpeting, updated bathrooms, updated closets, new windows, etc... Basically you can get the luxury finishes that you see in the brand new buildings for hundreds less in rent.', 'Property features secured entrances, video surveillance, laundry center, awesome dog park on site with city park 1 block away, plenty of off street parking.', "You can't beat the location.", 'Bordering New Hope, Crystal and Golden Valley and minutes to Honeywell and Centerpoint Energy facilities.', 'Minutes to West End in St Louis Park and downtown Minneapolis.', 'Bike path and Basset Creek Trail system right outside your door.', 'Bike to Medicine Lake, shops, etc.', 'Available 9/1', 'Video Tour:  https://youtu.be/xay6QnzGr5A', '** leasing special: 1 month free on a 12 month lease **']
